UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText` = 'You bring most welcome news $C. It is good to hear that Aynasha is alive and well thanks to you. I would hope that you might accept a reward for your valor. May Elune watch over you and light your path.' WHERE `entry` = 5713;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText` = 'The fighting is over!  I heard my daddy whisper to me.  He scared away all the ghosts and he says he\'s coming home!  I\'m so happy!$B$BHe also said I should welcome you if came to our house, so I made some tea!$B$BI hope you like lots of sugar!' WHERE `entry` = 5721;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText` = 'The body looks seriously beaten by clubs or fists, but most of the corpse\'s clothing and equipment still looks present. It seems the troggs do not overly care much for material wealth.$B$BYou begin to search the body for anything of interest that might help Magatha.' WHERE `entry` = 5722;
